# gradle

List available tasks of a project
```
gradle -q tasks [--all]
```

Dependency insights of an Android project
```
gradlew :app:dependencyInsight --configuration [debug|release]compileClasspath --dependency <dependency>
# For a project with product flavours
gradlew :app:dependencyInsight --configuration flavour[Debug|Release]compileClasspath --dependency <dependency>
```
